name: THE ONLY WAY TO GET TO AMSTERDAM? Stena Line Rail and Sail
description:
I took the Stena Line Rail and Sail from London to Amsterdam onboard the Stena Britannica. At the moment it's the only direct way to get from London to Amsterdam.
